{"tid":1280724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登又發生大型炒車事件","createTime":"2019-07-03T05:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T21:30:47.000Z","uid":254809,"like":1,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"53dd992e5d19819bc5c4eaf5c1494bb35a5934d8","tid":1280724,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"【Cloudflare 癱瘓】測試規則出錯 連登高登死機 23 分鐘<br />\n<br />\n網域代管公司 Cloudflare 尋晚服務一度陷於癱瘓，客戶嘅網站喺 23 分鐘內完全無法連線，包括香港嘅連登、高登、BabyKingdom 討論區，以及立場新聞等網站。好多人懷疑 Cloudflare 受到國家級 DDoS 攻擊，流量大到 Cloudflare 無法負荷。<br />\n實際上經 Cloudflare 調查後，原來只係誤會一場，Cloudflare CTO John Graham-Cumming 澄清話今次事件只係因為內部進行阻擋 Javascript 網絡攻擊嘅測試，希望透過 regex（regular expression） 去統計 false positive 率，但由於程式內其中一條規則出錯，導致全球伺服器嘅 CPU 用量飇升至 100%，先至令服務陷於癱瘓，客戶嘅網站無法登入，但就絕對同 DDoS 攻擊無關。<br />\n雖然即刻走出嚟道歉，不過就有唔少人喺留言度批評點解會出現咁低級嘅錯誤？係咪唔識做完 testing 至出街？有人仲乘機抽水話唔應該靠晒一間供應商，鼓勵大家分散風險咁話。<br />\n<br />\nLINK：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/548097535582470/posts/914991235559763/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F548097535582470%2Fposts%2F914991235559763%2F&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=94e538d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/548097535582470/posts/914991235559763/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原來唔關中國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a8ff78a088e829ccbe3f873c8a09e86e6148d44f","tid":1280724,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be1b3a4b8246a6e22888a891d85f1f8981a623f","tid":1280724,"uid":226955,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:24:34.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過代理人戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbaa48ae856108394ec8ab1e631905d1f0b7ebf","tid":1280724,"uid":260312,"like":0,"di